{
  "stem": "6944.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Renia kept on coming to the house, and then she befriended me personally.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she asked me if I have some beau, some gentleman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I do go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have many young people here, refugees as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- it's not a monastic life that I'm leading.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then-- there-- there's really nobody for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All we want to do now is that ORT-- we want to go to South America because we can't get into North America.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was gesperrt.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was closed for Jews, especially, and Canada, definitely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so we thought, well, we go to-- to South America where they speak Spanish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we'll work our way up to-- to USA, because we wanted to go to the USA to-- I don't know why, but that was in our minds.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So the ORT again started working, that we should be able to go to South America, to Montevideo, which is Uruguay, or to Para-- what-- whatever you call these places-- Chile, or-- these Spanish-- to Spanish-speaking places.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Argentina was out of bounds.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But Uruguay, Paraguay.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Chile and others.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These-- in the middle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not developed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There, they would allow Jews to come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so the ORT was working for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, you needed passage on a boat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were willing to pay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- the money was there for the-- for the refugees.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were wonderful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they said if you would go singly or in pairs, it would be easier to get on because a family of five is not-- not easy.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We refused.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were silly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We want to go as a family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were already separated twice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "No, thank you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We want to go as a family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they worked for it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
